                    <span>This book gives a clear overview over the board topic of MultiAgent Systems. Explainations are easy to follow and the references at the back of the book are particularly useful for those who want to dig deeper into any specific topic. This book itself will not make one an expert in the field but it provide all necessary knowledge for further independent study.<br>Very easy to read even for students with English as a second language, ideal for use as a text book at university level.<br>(I'm a post-graduate engineering student)</span>
                  
              
